y faith? </div><div class="t m9d2 x27 h4c y13d0 ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m1369 x4a h4c y13d0 ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What has obedience to God&apos;s law by faith in Christ done for </div><div class="t m627 x4a h4c y7a5 ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">you personally? What and where would you be today if you </div><div class="t m19a9 x4a h4c ya0d ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">had not accepted the will of God as stated in His law? </div><div class="t m38f xc4 h87 y1fc4 ff1 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">SUMMARY: </div><div class="t m1142 x3f h4c y1fc4 ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God&apos;s law, commandments, and statutes are not bur-</div><div class="t m24f xc4 h4c yf97 ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">densome. The secret is to have them in the heart, which will be a </div><div class="t mb95 xc4 h4c y10c7 ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">delight and make it a pleasure to obey them. </div><div class="t m21eb x4e h1e1 y18a7 ff7 fs12 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Don&apos;t ask that dollar where it went; </div><div class="t m8b4 x40 h1e1 ycd7 ff7 fs12 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Tell it where to go! </div><div class="t m3f26 x7 h87 y1d1a ff1 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">— H. </div><div class="t m1841 x23 h4c y1bef ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">D. Singleton </div><div class="t m141a x4a h8 ya65 ff4 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Send your dollars off for this quarter&apos;s Thirteenth </div><div class="t m636 x4a h8 yc48 ff4 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sabbath projects on the back cover. </div><div class="t m2360 xad h14f y1db7 ff7 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Twenty</div><div class="t m32b1 x75 hfa y758 ff7 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">-</div><div class="t m2453 xc0 h14f y758 ff7 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">five </div><div class="t mdb6 x14 h14f y1063 ff7 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">percent of the offering will support these projects. </div><div class="t m15ae xfd h27 yb6a ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">75 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
